                    IP-Link project news
        
        0.2: 2012-02-05
            This version introduces the generation of Bézier curves.
            It is now possible to see the relations between IP and ports.
            The tutorial has been updated.
        
        0.1: 2010-03-18
            First official release of IP-Link.
           
        
